creator: PinkNews Media Group Limited
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the PinkNews app, an inclusive space for the queer community and their allies. Bringing you all the latest lesbian, gay, bisexual, transgender (and more) stories straight to your device, 24/7.


Download our brand NEW app now for:

- LGBT+ news and views from around the world

- Real-life stories from the community

- Celebrity gossip and entertainment news

Plus the app also works in landscape so you can enjoy it on your phone or tablet, whichever way you like!

Coming soon...
Stay tuned. We’re constantly working on new updates for the app and we love to hear from you, our lovely readers. Please send your feedback or any new feature requests you have to appfeedback@pinknews.co.uk

PinkNews is the brand for the global LGBT+ community and the next generation. Our mission is to inform, inspire change and empower people to be themselves.

title: PinkNews

creator: PinkNews Media Group Limited
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the all-new PinkNews app, an inclusive space for the queer community and their allies. Bringing you all the latest lesbian, gay, bisexual, transgender (and more) news stories straight to your phone, 24/7.

Download the PinkNews app and enjoy brand new features including::

- Set your preferences to create a personalized newsfeed with only the topics you are most interested in
- Use our “Uplifting Stories” filter to only show you good news stories, for a happy-vibes-only experience

Plus we’re still bringing you..
- LGBTQ+ news and views from around the world
- Real-life stories from the queer community
- Celebrity gossip, entertainment and gaming news

PinkNews is the brand for the global LGBTQ+ community and the next generation bringing you a progressive, inclusive and uncompromising voice which represents the views and concerns of socially aware citizens. Our mission is to inform, inspire change and empower people to be themselves.

Stay tuned. We’re constantly working on new updates for the app but we love to hear from our readers. Please send your feedback or new feature requests to appfeedback@pinknews.co.uk

Terms and conditions for MyPinkNews can be found here: https://www.pinknews.co.uk/mypinknews/terms-conditions/

Welcome to the all-new PinkNews app, an inclusive space for the queer community and their allies. Bringing you all the latest lesbian, gay, bisexual, transgender (and more) news stories straight to your phone, 24/7.

Download the PinkNews app and enjoy brand new features including::

- Set your preferences to create a personalized newsfeed with only the topics you are most interested in
- Use our “Uplifting Stories” filter to only show you good news stories, for a happy-vibes-only experience

Plus we’re still bringing you..
- LGBTQ+ news and views from around the world
- Real-life stories from the queer community
- Celebrity gossip, entertainment and gaming news

PinkNews is the brand for the global LGBTQ+ community and the next generation bringing you a progressive, inclusive and uncompromising voice which represents the views and concerns of socially aware citizens. Our mission is to inform, inspire change and empower people to be themselves.

Stay tuned. We’re constantly working on new updates for the app but we love to hear from our readers. Please send your feedback or new feature requests to appfeedback@pinknews.co.uk

Terms and conditions for MyPinkNews can be found here: https://www.pinknews.co.uk/mypinknews/terms-conditions/

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Thanks so much for your feedback on the new app. We're still fine-tuning a few things and your comments have been very helpful. This release contains a bug fix to reduce crashes and various other improvements. Enjoy! We hope you like it, please feel free to share your feedback with us at appfeedback@pinknews.co.uk
